description: Efforts to repatriate Manx residents have not been "perfect' but are necessary, says chief minister.
title: Coronavirus: UK cases 'biggest threat' to Isle of Man's Covid-19 response
title_page: Coronavirus: UK cases 'biggest threat' to Isle of Man's Covid-19 response - BBC News
maintext: He added that the scheme was "being continuously reviewed" and may be amended in the next two weeks but only "when we have good medical data".
